{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Outrun eternity. Endlessly.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/gameplaybanner.gif?t=1730451701\" /><strong> </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The FIRST DREAM featuring 5 songs, IS AVAILABLE NOW IN THE DEMO!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">HYPERBEAT is a rhythm game with an original soundtrack, workshop support, and easy to learn but hard to master gameplay. Use your weapon of choice to slash your way through jungle and rave inspired beats, with each note flying at you indicating whether you slash, ride, or dodge your way through an endless dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/wellspringbanner.gif?t=1730451701\" />  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No rhythm game experience required! Play at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a visually stunning space and meet the KNIGHTS that embody the WELLSPRING.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your KNIGHT as you progress through the adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original soundtrack with a progression system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Custom charts with workshop integration will be available in the final release.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast paced rhythm gameplay with both mouse, controller, and tablet support.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Difficulties and accessibility options to tailor your gaming experience to your preferences.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263360/extras/chattingbanner.gif?t=1730451701\"